Test Case ID: TC-005

Title:
Verify cart count decreases after removal

Preconditions:
1. User is successfully signed in.
2. User in on the Cart page with items in the cart.

Test Steps:
1. Choose an item on the Cart page and click Remove
2. Choose a second item on the Cart page and click Remove
3. Choose a third item on the Cart page and click Remove

Expected Result:
1. Cart icon in top right will display correct number of items in cart
